Firstly, I am not sure if I do understand the exact usage of Rest Catalog, I believe that the Rest Catalog can wrap any existing Iceberg catalog implementation right? And I also refer to this peice of code, just replace the CATALOG IMPL from JdbcCatalog to HadoopCatalog (and the corresponding settings)
```
// Fallback to a JDBCCatalog impl if one is not set
    catalogProperties.putIfAbsent(
